OL,3,CNext ad banned for featuring
OL,4,C'unhealthily thin' model
OL,6,FAn advert for high street giant Next
OL,7,Fhas been banned for featuring a model
OL,8,Fwho appeared to be "unhealthily thin".
OL,10,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,11,F(ASA) said the "irresponsible" ad used
OL,12,Fthe camera angle and styling as well
OL,13,Fas the model's pose to emphasise the
OL,14,Fslimness of her legs.
OL,16,FThe ad, a product listing for denim
OL,17,Fleggings on the Next website in
OL,18,FSeptember, showed the model sitting on
OL,19,Fa wooden block with her legs extended
OL,20,Ftowards the camera.
