OL,6,FA single viewer complained that the ad
OL,7,Fwas irresponsible.
OL,9,FNext said the ad was created with a
OL,10,F"strong sense of responsibility to
OL,11,Fboth consumers and society" and the
OL,12,Fmodel, while slim, had a healthy and
OL,13,Ftoned physique that aligned with the
OL,14,Fnature of its product.
OL,16,FThe retailer confirmed it had not
OL,17,Fapplied digital retouching to alter
OL,18,Fthe model's appearance, but said the
OL,19,Fimage of the leggings was altered so
OL,20,Fthey were brought further down towards
OL,21,Fher ankles.
