OL,6,FNext said its stylist and product
OL,7,Fimage manager met the model in person
OL,8,Fand did not have any concerns about
OL,9,Fher health.
OL,11,FThe ASA acknowledged that the model's
OL,12,Fface did not appear to be gaunt and
OL,13,Fher arms, while slim, did not display
OL,14,Fany protruding bones.
