OL,6,FHowever, it said the model's left leg
OL,7,Fwas bent at a right angle, with her
OL,8,Fthigh appearing to be the same width
OL,9,Fas her lower leg, and the sharpness of
OL,10,Fthe angle drawing attention to her
OL,11,Fknee, which was prominent underneath
OL,12,Fthe tight-fitting leggings.
OL,14,FThe shot appeared to have been taken
OL,15,Ffrom a lower angle, which accentuated
OL,16,Fthe model's already tall physique and
OL,17,Ffurther emphasised the slimness of her
OL,18,Flegs.
