OL,6,FFurthermore, the pointed shape of her
OL,7,Fshoes, as well as their positioning,
OL,8,Fadded to the impression of the model's
OL,9,Felongated legs, which accentuated
OL,10,Ftheir slimness.
OL,12,FOther photos of the model within the
OL,13,Fsame product listing showed her in
OL,14,Fdifferent positions and from different
OL,15,Fangles, and she did not appear to be
OL,16,Funhealthily thin in these additional
OL,17,Fimages, the ASA said.
