OL,6,FThe watchdog said: "Because the pose,
OL,7,Fcamera angle and styling in the ad
OL,8,Finvestigated strongly emphasised the
OL,9,Fslimness of the model's legs, we
OL,10,Fconsidered that the ad gave the
OL,11,Fimpression that the model was
OL,12,Funhealthily thin.
OL,14,F"For the above reasons, we concluded
OL,15,Fthat the ad was irresponsible."
