OL,6,FThe ASA ruled that the ad must not
OL,7,Fappear again in its current form,
OL,8,Fadding: "We told Next to ensure that
OL,9,Fthe images in their ads were prepared
OL,10,Fresponsibly and did not portray models
OL,11,Fas being unhealthily thin."
